Design patterns in microservices:
---> There are multiple design patterns in microservices, But i know some of them.

1. API Gateway Design pattern:

API Gateway Design pattern provides single entry point for clients to route the requests to particular microservices. It act as front controller to route the traffic to multiple microservices.


2. Databse per microservices;

----> In database per microservcies, Each microservice has its own database which ensures loose coupling and independent data management.

3. Circuit breaker pattern:

---> 

4. SAGA design pattern

5. Service discovery Design pattern: 

---> In service discovrey pattern, Microservices get registered with service registery so that microservices can communictae with each other.


